#: ../../D/dentro.rst:9
msgid ""
"[ :ref:`demoscene`\\] Combination of :ref:`demo` (sense 4) and "
":ref:`intro`\\. Other name mixings include intmo, dentmo etc. and are used "
"usually when the authors are not quite sure whether the program is a "
":ref:`demo` or an :ref:`intro`\\. Special-purpose coinages like wedtro (some"
" member of a group got married), invtro (invitation intro) etc. have also "
"been sighted."
msgstr ""
"[\\ :ref:`demoscene`\\ ] \\ :ref:`demo`\\ (語義4)と\\ :ref:`intro`\\ "
"の組み合わせ。他の名前の混合にはintmo、dentmoなどがあり、通常は作者がそのプログラムが\\ :ref:`demo`\\ なのか\\ "
":ref:`intro`\\ "
"なのか確信が持てないときに使われる。wedtro(グループのメンバーの誰かが結婚した)、invtro(招待用のintro)などの特殊用途の造語も目撃されている。"
